data.description: This is a great opportunity to acquire lovely HOME, very conveniently situated near major transportation and shopping centers minutes away from OUTLES Stores.  The property has 2-car garage, driveway for 2 cars or trucks, front yard has beautiful garden with variance of flowers, have cover patio with many herbs' garden, flower, concrete around the house minimum maintenance on the back yard. The home features 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, laminated flooring throughout. The kitchen cabinets are on good conditions. beautiful chimney and nice view. property have a resent install new roof that also including garage and cover patio, new water heater and new air condition system, the house have recently new paint from outside. The property has solar panels, buyer needs to assume the lease. payment is ($110.40) monthly.
